CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 5, 1955, pg. 13A, reads: "Mr. and Mrs. Luvernis Lee...they toast each other. - Harris Photo." Portion of accompanying article reads: "Helen Lee is Surprised by Husband on Gala Birthday - Pittsburgh's ace host, Luvernis Lee, surprised his wife Helen on her birthday, Oct. 28, with one of the most exciting parties given in this city in recent weeks..."
TitMainTitle: Luvernis Lee toasting Helen "Honey" Lee on her birthday, in front of stairs in their home
